<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.4.4">
<l>kompuma ravamum valliyum veṉṟanuṇ ṇēriṭai</l>
<l>vampuṇ kuḻalār vācala ṭaittika ḻātamuṉ</l>
<l>cempoṉka mukiṉan tāṉkaṉi yumceḻuñ cōlaicūḻ</l>
<l>nampaṉ naṟaiyūr nāmtoḻu tumeḻu neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before those with fragrant curls</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] lovely, thin waists that surpass</l>
<l>Serpents, twigs, and creeper vines, can scold, slamming the door,</l>
<l>Arise, [my] heart! We will worship in the noble’s Naṟaiyūr</l>
<l>Encircled by fertile groves where clusters of rose-gold areca ripen.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
